fields.company_name: Webbytes Sdn Bhd  (POS System) |  Jakarta & Kuala Lumpur
fields.details:
Successfully managed the end-to-end project for the launch of a new store, coordinating with cross-functional teams, vendors, and stakeholders, resulting in a seamless and on-time store opening.
	Implemented efficient project management processes, such as clear communication channels, regular progress tracking, and issue resolution mechanisms, ensuring effective coordination and collaboration among teams, and minimizing delays or bottlenecks.
	Led the development and implementation of a software training program, equipping team of stakeholders with essential skills and tools, resulting in improved project outcomes.
